Constructor Detail

SubmissionFeedback

public SubmissionFeedback(double correctness,
                          int timeOnTask,
                          S additionalData,
                          Component feedbackComponent,
                          SubmissionType submType)
Constructs a new SubmissionFeedback-object with no additional feedback-component.

Parameters:
correctness - correctness value of the submission in the range 0.0 - 1.0
timeOnTask - time on task in seconds (from submission to submission; reseting the exercise state should not reset the timer)
additionalData - exercise-type specific additional info as a suitable SubmissionInfo-object
feedbackComponent - Component that can be shown to the user as additional visual feedback on the submission just made
